com.example.buber.Model

Class Trip

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.buber.Model.Trip

  • public class Trip
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a trip a rider is wishing to take. Stores two locations, one for the start and end. Status represents the current status of the trip (pending is before a driver accepts, then driveraccept, then inprogress, and cancelled if a user chooses to do so).
